		<title>Targeting and Pitching Bloggers: With Pro Blogger Darren Rowse</title>
		<link>http://allindiewriters.com/darren-rowse-pitching-bloggers/</link>
		<comments>http://allindiewriters.com/darren-rowse-pitching-bloggers/#comments</comments>
